_sText:
Sorry for the late upload, my life has be very busy recently

This map was featured in the third week of BHWC 2020

I decided to keep the displacement skip on the blacktop stage, I like the route variation it adds.

Thank you to everyone who gave the map a shot. I know my mapping style isn't for everyone. This will more than likely be my final bhop map. I might come back eventually, we'll see what happens. Mapping has been one of my favorite pass times for a long period of my life. I don't know, I just appreciate all you guys.
